    <string name="sobre_titulo">About the App</string>
    <string name="sobre_descricao">Cruzeiro EcoSul is an educational app created to encourage sustainable practices in everyday life. Our goal is to raise awareness and inspire people to care for the planet through small actions that lead to great change.</string>

